title: MarginCallResponseTypeEnum
description: Represents the enumeration values to define the response type to a margin call.

oneOf.title: AgreeinFull
oneOf.description: Specifies a 'Full Agreement' to Margin Call.

oneOf.title: Dispute
oneOf.description: Specifies a 'Full Dispute' to a Margin call.

oneOf.title: PartiallyAgree
oneOf.description: Specifies a 'Partial agreement' to Margin Call.
